{"type":null,"faqId":37109,"title":"如何更新手环版本和APP版本？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:宋体;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>升级前，请确保手环和手机通过蓝牙正常连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>更新手环版本：在APP中点击左上角设置图标，点击“更新 TalkBand B2”，手环将会检测版本信息并更新。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>图示：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121739\" style=\"width:2.0416667in;height:3.629861in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span>更新APP版本：在APP中点击右上角小人图标，点击“关于 &gt; App版本更新”，当手机显示“更新...”时，即可检测APP版本信息并更新。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=121740\" style=\"width:2.0729167in;height:3.6868055in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  ></p>\n<p  >\n<span>说明：更新时，手环会自动断开蓝牙，请您耐心等待直至升级结束。</span>\n</p>\n<p  ></p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":212,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2273","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1440750143000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":164,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"华为手环,B2,手环更新,APP版本","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}